        ...    ${src['pass']}    ${src['container_type']}    ${src['container_name']}
    END
    Lists Should Be Equal    ${after_list}    ${before_list}
    Log    ${after_list}
    Log    ${before_list}
    Run Keyword and Ignore Error    Collect Logs

